Package: forestr
Title: Forest Management Tools, Primarily for the Province of British Columbia, Canada
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Colin", "Chisholm", , "colin.chisholm@unbc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(website = "http://chisholm.forestecosystems.ca"))
Description: Forest management tools for strategic and operational forest planning 
    (e.g. Timber Supply Analysis and Site Planning repectively). Includes
    tools for collecting spatial data from the BC Data Catelogue via 
    [`bcdata`](https://github.com/bcgov/bcdata), manipulating spatial data for 
    creating a _resultant_, creating field sampling plans, and managing GPS data.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    bcdata,
    leaflet,
    magrittr,
    mapedit,
    sf
